high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the front of the brown shelf with the cardboard box on it.
Pick up the credit card that is on top of the shelf to the right of the cardboard box.
Turn to the left, go across the room, turn to the left and go to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card and turn on a lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wooden shelves on the right.
Pick up the blue credit card to the right of the box.
Turn left and hang a left at the wall to reach the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the shelf with the empty box on it.
Grab the credit card on the shelf.
Turn left and walk to the lamp in the corner of the room to your left.
anns.task_desc: Grab the credit card and turn on the lamp in the corner of the room.
